casebody.data:
Frank Delano WHITEHEAD Aka Neal Deon Lucas
v.
STATE of North Carolina. No. 78P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 3, 2005. Frank Delano Whitehead, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, C. Colon Willoughby, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 3rd day of February 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Wake County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of March 2005."
